== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
迪士尼對{{link-en|美女與野獸 (音樂劇)|Beauty and the Beast (musical)|1994年百老匯音樂劇}}進行電影改編的工作為發展揭開序幕<ref>{{cite web|title=Alan Menken Adesso musicalanche in Italia|url=http://www.lastampa.it/2009/06/05/spettacoli/alan-menken-adesso-musical-anche-in-italia-tpFNsKZZjpc7PLwUeVEkKM/pagina.html|accessdate=2015-05-21|date=2009-06-05|last=Marmiroli|first=Adriana|work={{link-en|新聞報 (義大利)|La Stampa|La Stampa}}|language=it|archive-url=https://archive.today/20150524013613/http://www.lastampa.it/2009/06/05/spettacoli/alan-menken-adesso-musical-anche-in-italia-tpFNsKZZjpc7PLwUeVEkKM/pagina.html|archive-date=2015-05-24|dead-url=no|trans-title=Alan Menken musicals now in Itaty}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Hollywood bets big on 'Beast,' considers remake of 'My Fair Lady'|url=http://jimhillmedia.com/blogs/jim_hilll/archive/2009/07/01/hollywood-bets-big-on-beast-considers-remake-of-my-fair-lady.aspx|accessdate=2015-05-21|date=2009-07-01|last=Hill|first=Jim|work=Jim Hill Media|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090704035305/http://jimhillmedia.com/blogs/jim_hilll/archive/2009/07/01/hollywood-bets-big-on-beast-considers-remake-of-my-fair-lady.aspx|archive-date=2009-07-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，在2011年的採訪中，作曲家[[亞倫·孟肯|亞倫·孟肯]]表示，將《美女與野獸》音樂劇版本改編成電影的計畫「被裝罐」<ref>{{cite web|title=Alan Menken interview: Tangled, movie scores, musicals, Enchanted 2, Snow Queen and more|url=http://www.denofgeek.com/movies/725326/alan_menken_interview_tangled_movie_scores_musicals_enchanted_2_snow_queen_and_more.html|accessdate=2011-01-22|date=2011-01-11|last=Brew|first=Simon|publisher={{link-en|丹尼斯出版社|Dennis Publishing|Den of Geek}}|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130121113312/http://www.denofgeek.com/movies/725326/alan_menken_interview_tangled_movie_scores_musicals_enchanted_2_snow_queen_and_more.html|archive-date=2013-01-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

到2014年4月，[[華特迪士尼影業|華特迪士尼影業]]已開始開發一部重拍自《[[美女与野兽_(1991年电影)|美女與野獸]]》的真人動作電影，其作業在其他真人奇幻電影如《[[魔境夢遊|魔境夢遊]]》、《[[黑魔女：沉睡魔咒|黑魔女：沉睡魔咒]]》、《[[仙履奇緣_(2015年電影)|仙履奇緣]]》和《[[與森林共舞|與森林共舞]]》後進行<ref>{{cite news|last1=Chitwood|first1=Adam|title=Rumor: Could Bill Condon Direct Disney's Live-Action BEAUTY AND THE BEAST?|url=http://collider.com/beauty-and-the-beast-bill-condon/|accessdate=2015-05-20|publisher=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|date=2014-04-11|archive-url=https://archive.today/20150524013704/http://collider.com/beauty-and-the-beast-bill-condon/|archive-date=2015-05-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月，[[比爾·坎登|比爾·坎登]]簽署執導電影，{{link-en|埃文·斯皮里奧托普洛斯|Evan Spiliotopoulos}}編劇<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=Bill Condon to Direct Live-Action 'Beauty and the Beast' Film for Disney|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/bill-condon-beauty-and-the-beast-disney-1201151834/|accessdate=2015-01-27|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2014-06-04|archive-url=https://archive.li/20170910095143/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/bill-condon-beauty-and-the-beast-disney-1201151834/|archive-date=2017-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月，[[史蒂芬·切波斯基|史蒂芬·切波斯基]]受聘重寫劇本<ref>{{cite web|title='Perks of Being a Wallflower' author will adapt 'Beauty and the Beast'|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/09/29/perks-of-being-a-wallflower-stephen-chbosky-beauty-and-the-beast/|accessdate=2014-09-30|date=2014-09-29|last=Sperling|first=Nicole|publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141001025146/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/09/29/perks-of-being-a-wallflower-stephen-chbosky-beauty-and-the-beast/|archive-date=2014-10-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===
2015年1月，[[艾瑪·華森|艾瑪·華生]]宣布她將飾演女主角{{link-en|貝兒 (迪士尼)|Belle (Disney)|貝兒}}<ref name="WatsonCast" />。3月，[[路克·伊凡斯|路克·伊凡斯]]和[[丹·史蒂文斯|丹·史蒂文斯]]在會談中透露，兩人分別詮釋{{link-en|加斯頓 (迪士尼)|Gaston (Disney)|加斯頓}}與{{link-en|野獸 (迪士尼)|Beast (Disney)|野獸}}<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|script-title=en:Luke Evans to Play Gaston in Disney’s ‘Beauty and the Beast’ (EXCLUSIVE)|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/luke-evans-to-play-gaston-in-disneys-beauty-and-the-beast-1201446186/|accessdate=2015-03-09|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2015-03-04|archive-url=https://archive.li/20150304220328/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/luke-evans-to-play-gaston-in-disneys-beauty-and-the-beast-1201446186/|archive-date=2015-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title=Disney's 'Beauty and the Beast' Casting Dan Stevens as the Beast (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/disneys-beauty-beast-casts-dan-779323|accessdate=2015-03-09|publisher=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2015-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150305215127/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/disneys-beauty-beast-casts-dan-779323|archive-date=2015-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>，華森於隔天透過[[推特|推文]]證實他們的角色<ref name="StevensCast" /><ref name="EvansCast" />。其他主要演員——[[喬許·蓋德|喬許·蓋德]]、[[艾瑪·湯普遜|艾瑪·湯普遜]]、[[凱文·克萊|凱文·克萊]]、[[奧黛莉·麥唐娜|奧黛莉·麥唐娜]]、[[伊恩·麥克連|伊恩·麥克連]]、[[古古·瑪芭塔-勞|古古·瑪芭塔-勞]]、[[伊旺·麥奎格|伊旺·麥奎格]]和[[史丹利·圖奇|史丹利·圖奇]]於同年3月至4月間確認將分別飾演樂福、茶壺夫人、莫里斯、葛德蘿、葛士華、蓓特、盧米亞及卡丹薩<ref name="ReleaseThompsonKline" /><ref name="GadCast" /><ref name="McGregorCast" /><ref name="TucciCast" /><ref name="McKellenCast" /><ref name="McDonaldCast" /><ref name="RawCast" /><ref>{{cite web|title=Q & A|url=http://decoy.tvpassport.com/q_a/q-january-i-read-emma-watson-was-star-disneys-live-action-beauty-and-beast-film-and-production-w?subid=national-00001|accessdate=2015-08-03|last=Thomlison|first=Adam|publisher=TV Media|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003043039/http://decoy.tvpassport.com/q_a/q-january-i-read-emma-watson-was-star-disneys-live-action-beauty-and-beast-film-and-production-w?subid=national-00001|archive-date=2015-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

於《美女與野獸》百老匯版本中飾演貝兒的{{link-en|蘇珊·伊根|Susan Egan}}，在選角期間評論華森為「完美的」<ref>{{cite web|title=Original Broadway 'Belle' Susan Egan Comments on Emma Watson in BEAUTY AND THE BEAST|url=http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Original-Broadway-Belle-Susan-Egan-Comments-on-Emma-Watson-in-BEAUTY-AND-THE-BEAST-20150126|accessdate=2015-08-11|date=2015-01-26|work=Broadway World|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170910101739/https://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Original-Broadway-Belle-Susan-Egan-Comments-on-Emma-Watson-in-BEAUTY-AND-THE-BEAST-20150126|archive-date=2017-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而於動畫電影及其續集裡為貝兒配音的{{link-en|佩吉·奧哈拉|Paige O'Hara}}，表示願意在歌唱方面協助華森<ref>{{cite web|title=Paige O'Hara wants to teach Emma Watson|url=http://watsonuncensored.blogspot.com/2015/02/paige-ohara-wants-to-teach-emma-watson.html|accessdate=2015-08-11|date=2015-02-04|work=Emma Watson Updates|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304233033/http://watsonuncensored.blogspot.com/2015/02/paige-ohara-wants-to-teach-emma-watson.html|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

