=== 同性戀情節風波 ===
2017年電影版本的故事中，來富（[[喬許·蓋德|喬許·蓋德]]飾演）在插曲《Gaston》期間的演出，被設定有[[同性戀|同性戀]]傾向，代表著迪士尼電影裡第一位同性戀角色<ref>{{cite web|title=Beauty and the Beast: Disney's First Gay Character Is Here|url=http://time.com/4686896/disney-beauty-beast-emma-watson-dan-stevens-gay-character/|accessdate=2017-03-03|date=2017-03-01|publisher=Time.com|archive-url=https://archive.li/20170301225912/http://time.com/4686896/disney-beauty-beast-emma-watson-dan-stevens-gay-character/|archive-date=2017-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

該決定已得到讚揚及部分批評的聲音<ref>{{cite web|title=Why 'Beauty and the Beast's gay character is not as groundbreaking as Disney believes|url=https://www.dailydot.com/parsec/disney-beauty-beast-gay-character-lefou-gaston/|accessdate=2017-03-03|date=|publisher=The Daily Dot|archive-url=https://archive.li/20170306181459/https://www.dailydot.com/parsec/disney-beauty-beast-gay-character-lefou-gaston/|archive-date=2017-03-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]政府原本考慮禁映電影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/global/russia-ban-beauty-and-the-beast-josh-gad-gay-lefou-1202002198/|accessdate=2017-03-05|date=2017-03-04|publisher=Variety|archive-url=https://archive.li/20170419053121/http://variety.com/2017/film/global/russia-ban-beauty-and-the-beast-josh-gad-gay-lefou-1202002198/|archive-date=2017-04-19|dead-url=no|script-title=en:Russia May Ban Disney’s ‘Beauty and the Beast’ Over Gay Character}}</ref>，但後來轉而決定禁止16歲以下的人在劇院觀賞該片<ref>{{cite web|title=Russia won't ban Beauty and the Beast — but will have an age restriction|url=http://ew.com/movies/2017/03/06/beauty-and-the-beast-russia-lawmaker-ban/|accessdate=2017-03-07|date=2017-03-06|publisher=Entertainment Weekly|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170910205642/http://ew.com/movies/2017/03/06/beauty-and-the-beast-russia-lawmaker-ban/|archive-date=2017-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，因為其插曲《Gaston》，包含美國阿拉巴馬州[[黑纳格_(阿拉巴马州)|黑納格]]的一些劇院將不會放映電影<ref>{{cite web|title=Alabama Theater Won't Show 'Beauty And The Beast' Because Of Gay Subplot|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/beauty-and-the-beast-alabama-theater_us_58b9a6f7e4b05cf0f400427b|accessdate=2017-03-03|date=|publisher=The Huffington Post|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170306104238/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/beauty-and-the-beast-alabama-theater_us_58b9a6f7e4b05cf0f400427b|archive-date=2017-03-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在馬來西亞，[[馬來西亞電影審查委員會|電影審查委員會]]堅持涉同性戀情節的場景應被刪減，促使迪士尼將上映日期無限期推遲，隨後，若該片無法不經審查，迪士尼將把電影完全撤出馬來西亞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2017/03/13/beauty-and-the-beast-release-postponed-for-internal-review/|accessdate=2017-03-15|date=2017-03-13|last=Cheang|first=Michael|website=The Star Online|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170314040844/http://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2017/03/13/beauty-and-the-beast-release-postponed-for-internal-review/|archive-date=2017-03-14|dead-url=no|script-title=en:Beauty and the Beast release postponed for ‘internal review’}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Disney pulls Beauty and the Beast from cinemas in Malaysia "until further notice"|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/beauty-and-the-beast/news/a823340/disney-pulls-beauty-and-the-beast-from-cinemas-in-malaysi-until-further-notice/|accessdate=2017-03-13|date=2017-03-13|publisher=Digital Spy|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170910204933/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/beauty-and-the-beast/news/a823340/disney-pulls-beauty-and-the-beast-from-cinemas-in-malaysi-until-further-notice/|archive-date=2017-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/disney-refuses-to-cut-gay-moment-from-beauty-and-the-beast-for-malaysia|accessdate=2017-03-15|date=2017-03-15|website=Malay Mail Online|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170910205012/http://www.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/disney-refuses-to-cut-gay-moment-from-beauty-and-the-beast-for-malaysia|archive-date=2017-09-10|dead-url=no|script-title=en:Disney refuses to cut ‘gay moment’ from ‘Beauty and the Beast’ for Malaysia}}</ref>。該工作室將發布日期移至3月30日，以讓馬來西亞的電影審查委員會有更多時間作出是否在不進行刪減的情況下發行電影的決定<ref>{{cite web|title=Disney Defies Malaysia Censors, Won't Cut 'Beauty and the Beast' Gay Moment|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/disney-wont-cut-beauty-beast-gay-moment-malaysia-censors-986609|accessdate=2017-03-16|author=Mia Galuppo|date=2017-03-15|publisher=''[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]''|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170910205050/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/disney-wont-cut-beauty-beast-gay-moment-malaysia-censors-986609|archive-date=2017-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马来西亚最终决定在不删剪的情况下以PG-13的方式播出。

